# UI Guidelines

## Color Scheme
The app uses a dark theme with these primary colors:

```dart
// From lib/core/constants/app_colors.dart
class AppColors {
  static const primaryDark = Color(0xFF0A0A15);
  static const deepBlue = Color(0xFF1A1B3D);
  static const deepPurple = Color(0xFF2D0A47);
  static const accentPurple = Color(0xFFBB86FC);
  static const accentBlue = Color(0xFF3700B3);
  static const lightGray = Color(0xFFE0E0E0);
}
```

## UI Components

### Dynamic Island
- Used for status notifications
- Located at the top of the screen
- Shows current app status (e.g., "正在生成...", "任务已完成")

### Navigation
- Bottom tab bar with 4 sections:
  1. Creation (创作)
  2. Tasks (任务)
  3. Ideas (灵感)
  4. Settings (设置)
- No floating action button in the tab bar

### Cards and Containers
- Use rounded corners (borderRadius: 20)
- Semi-transparent backgrounds
- Subtle gradients
- Thin borders with low opacity

### Typography
- Use system fonts (no external fonts)
- Clear hierarchy with different sizes and weights
- High contrast for readability

### iOS-Specific
- Respect safe areas
- Account for notch and dynamic island
- Support saving comics to photo gallery
